text: Happy to be here with friends❣️ good Bao and roasted delights🥳🥳🥳

Highly recommended the Tzi Char stall Gim Seng Seafood. I haven't been here for long time and saw from food Panda that there's this new stall here ( or new coffee shop). Ordered via food delivery and love the food. Forgot to take pictures. Sambal Sotong Rice,Sambal Sweet Potato Leaf, Prawn omelette.. food was fresh and nice 👍👍👍
Eat whole food and eat delicious food.
